### Testes da API - Sistema Financeiro
### Para usar: instale a extensão REST Client no VS Code

### Variáveis de ambiente
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiVersion = v1

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 1. FORNECEDORES

### Listar todos os fornecedores
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/suppliers
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar novo fornecedor
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/suppliers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "company_name": "Tech Solutions Ltda",
    "trade_name": "TechSol",
    "tax_id": "12345678000190",
    "email": "contato@techsol.com.br",
    "phone": "(11) 9999-1234",
    "address": "Rua das Tecnologias, 123",
    "city": "São Paulo",
    "state": "SP",
    "postal_code": "01234-567"
}

###

### Buscar fornecedor por ID (substitua {id} pelo ID real)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/suppliers/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Atualizar fornecedor
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/suppliers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "company_name": "Tech Solutions Ltda - Atualizada",
    "trade_name": "TechSol Plus",
    "tax_id": "12345678000190",
    "email": "contato@techsolplus.com.br",
    "phone": "(11) 9999-1234",
    "address": "Rua das Tecnologias, 123",
    "city": "São Paulo", 
    "state": "SP",
    "postal_code": "01234-567"
}

###

### Soft delete de fornecedor
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/suppliers/1

###

