### 4. CONTAS A PAGAR

### Listar contas a pagar
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/payable-accounts
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar conta a pagar
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/payable-accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "supplier_id": 1,
    "invoice_number": "NF-001/2024",
    "issue_date": "2024-01-15",
    "due_date": "2024-02-15",
    "total_amount": 1500.00,
    "description": "Serviços de consultoria em TI",
    "account_type": "DESPESA",
    "expense_category": "SERVICOS_TERCEIROS",
    "installments_count": 1,
    "current_installment": 1
}

